er|3:10\n|rowspan=3|[[Las Vegas, Nevada]], United States\n|{{small|[[The Ultimate Fighter: Team Lesnar vs. Team dos Santos|The Ultimate Fighter 13]] Semi-Final round.}}\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|align=center|2\u20130\n|Ryan McGillivray\n|TKO (punches)\n|{{dts|2011|May|25}} (airdate)\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0:46\n|{{small|[[The Ultimate Fighter: Team Lesnar vs. Team dos Santos|The Ultimate Fighter 13]] Quarter-Final round.}}\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|align=center|1\u20130\n|[[Justin Edwards (fighter)|Justin Edwards]]\n|KO (upkick)\n|{{dts|2011|May|4}} (airdate)\n|align=center|1\n| align=center|3:56\n|{{small|[[The Ultimate Fighter: Team Lesnar vs. Team dos Santos|The Ultimate Fighter 13]] Preliminary round.}}\n{{end}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of current UFC fighters]]\n*[[List of male mixed martial artists]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Sherdog|31239}}\n*{{UFC|Tony-Ferguson}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ach|ach}}\n{{s-new}}\n{{s-ttl|title=1st [[List of UFC champions#Lightweight Championship|UFC Interim Lightweight Champion]]|years=October 7, 2017 - April 7, 2018<br>Stripped}}\n{{s-inc|Vacant}}\n{{end}}\n\n{{UFC Championships}}\n{{UFC Lightweight Championship}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ferguson, Tony}}\n[[Category:1984 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American male mixed martial artists]]\n[[Category:Mixed martial artists from California]]\n[[Category:American mixed martial artists of Mexican descent]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American sportspeople]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Oxnard, California]]\n[[Category:Grand Valley State University alumni]]\n[[Category:Lightweight mixed martial artists]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Muskegon, Michigan]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Ventura County, California]]\n[[Category:Ultimate Fighting Championship male fighters]]\n", "text_old": "{{for|the skateboarder|Tony Ferguson (skateboarder)}}\n{{pp-pc1}}\n{{short description|American mixed martial arts fighter}}\n{{Info